---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_100%_50%_at_50%_100%,rgba(120,80,255,0.08),transparent)]"></div>

	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
				From Idea to PR in
				<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 to-fuchsia-400">Minutes</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				No setup. No configuration. Just describe what you want and let Claude do the rest.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="relative">
			<div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-24 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-700 to-transparent"></div>

			<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
				<div class="relative">
					<div class="absolute -top-4 left-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
						01
					</div>
					<div class="pt-8">
						<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-fuchsia-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
							<i class="ph ph-link text-2xl text-violet-400"></i>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Connect Your Repo</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Paste any GitHub URL or browse your connected repositories. We support public and private repos.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="relative">
					<div class="absolute -top-4 left-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
						02
					</div>
					<div class="pt-8">
						<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-fuchsia-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
							<i class="ph ph-chat-circle-text text-2xl text-violet-400"></i>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Describe What You Want</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Tell Claude what you need in plain English. Fix a bug, add a feature, refactor code â€” anything.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="relative">
					<div class="absolute -top-4 left-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
						03
					</div>
					<div class="pt-8">
						<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-fuchsia-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
							<i class="ph ph-magic-wand text-2xl text-violet-400"></i>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Claude Writes Code</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Watch as Claude creates a feature branch, writes the code, and commits changes in real-time.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="relative">
					<div class="absolute -top-4 left-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-slate-400">
						04
					</div>
					<div class="pt-8">
						<div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-fuchsia-500/20 border border-violet-500/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
							<i class="ph ph-git-pull-request text-2xl text-violet-400"></i>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Review & Merge</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Get a notification when the PR is ready. Review the changes and merge directly from the app.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-16 text-center">
			<a href="#download" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-violet-400 hover:text-violet-300 font-medium transition-colors">
				Try it yourself
				<i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
